_aChangeLog.text: Fixed some textures not working linux due to a rare bug. Thanks Olivia and Malala!
Changed bonus sounds to use point_clientcommand so music will stop changing so often when spectating
Few small lighting and texture improvements

_sText:
A collaboration by the Mapzor server. Participants had 1 month to create a stage with any type of gameplay they like as long as it was possible on legit bhop settings (100 aa, stamina.)

There is at least one easter egg on each stage.
